As far as I'm concerned,
it's going to run forever.


1361
01:50:58.323 --> 01:51:01.158
- Tony.
- May we say something?


1362
01:51:01.659 --> 01:51:04.745
A show that is really a show

1363
01:51:04.954 --> 01:51:08.415
Sends you out with
a kind of a glow

1364
01:51:08.625 --> 01:51:12.377
And you say as
you go on your way

1365
01:51:13.505 --> 01:51:16.089
"That's entertainment!"

1366
01:51:16.925 --> 01:51:19.676
A song that is winging along

1367
01:51:19.886 --> 01:51:23.430
Or a dance with a touch of romance

1368
01:51:23.640 --> 01:51:27.226
Is the art that appeals to the heart

1369
01:51:28.436 --> 01:51:31.271
That's entertainment!

1370
01:51:31.481 --> 01:51:35.067
Admit we're a hit
And we'll go on from there


1371
01:51:35.276 --> 01:51:38.320
We played a charade
That was lighter than air


1372
01:51:39.489 --> 01:51:42.199
A good old-fashioned affair

1373
01:51:42.408 --> 01:51:45.953
As we sing this finale
We hope it was up your alley


1374
01:51:46.162 --> 01:51:49.373
No death like you get in Macbeth

1375
01:51:49.582 --> 01:51:52.960
No ordeal like the end of Camille

1376
01:51:53.169 --> 01:51:56.964
This good-bye brings a tear to the eye

1377
01:51:57.173 --> 01:52:00.801
The world is a stage
The stage is a world


1378
01:52:01.010 --> 01:52:07.724
Of entertainment